[DQR.IFRS.0129.9627] It is expected that ProfitLossAttributableToNoncontrollingInterests with a value of -56,700,000 reported in the network role https://unibel.fr/role/ProfitOrLoss should be equal to the dimensionally qualified concept, ProfitLoss with the dimension ifrs-full:ComponentsOfEquityAxis = ifrs-full:NoncontrollingInterestsMember and a reported value of 56,700,000 multiplied by 1. This value appears in the network role https://unibel.fr/role/StatChangesInEquity. This error occurs when the dimensionally qualified fact is not equal to the value input for the non dimensional item.
